Job Description:
Pricing & Data Analyst - Helloprint CONNECT
As Helloprint's Pricing & Data Analyst you will be responsible for the commercial execution of our pricing strategies. This will be a very challenging job: our business is in 23 countries and we have over 10 million unique products that require pricing. You will learn all the in's and out’s of the pricing business and you will make sure our product offering always has the most competitive pricing. You have the vision: where do we go with our pricing strategies? How can we improve our margins?

What you do
You will analyze all developments at our competition and signalize trends;
You will develop the best pricing models for all our customer target groups based on your analyses;
Generate pricing strategy hypotheses and establishing/implementing market price tests;
You will execute our pricing strategies for all our international websites;
You will maintain our pricing strategies by continuously checking and updating them;
You will make sure that our prices will differentiate us within the market;
You will bring new dashboards and insights to the company;
You will work on different projects that improve the scalability of our pricing tooling and pricing models.
You work together with other teams (Category Management, Marketing, Website Management) to sell more of our products

What we are looking for
A Bachelor's or Master’s Degree in Mathematics, Economics, Engineering, Operations Research, Statistics, Business or other related technical disciplines.
2+ years of experience working in a similar analytical role, ideally within a pricing or marketing team;
Your commercial and data drive helps you to see opportunities everywhere and you act on these immediately;
You have strong analytical skills and data has no secrets from you;
Work experience within an e-commerce environment is a plus;
You are an Excel-expert and preferably have experience with another software tooling.

What we offer
The possibility to learn and work at one of the fastest-growing e-commerce companies in Europe;
A unique possibility to have an amazing time in Europe’s coolest city;
An incredible office right next to Nuevo Centro Shopping Mall;
A team of 60 amazing colleagues with different nationalities;

Are you up for it?
Apply now and let us know why you are the perfect match for our team!

Welcome to Helloprint. Design Yourself.

