PERFORMANCE ANALYST

Role:
Design KPIs and relevant dashboards defined by business key users;
Automate data extraction and transformation to feed dashboards from various data sources;
Administrate, monitor and support the BI & Visualization platform;
Assist in designing, planning and managing data and report migration processes;
Assist Key users to select statistical analysis tools;
Provide technical assistance and training to internal customers;
Bring continuous improvement to data consistency, modeling and performance.

Profile:
Bachelor/Master's degree in Computer Science or related field;
Demonstrated experience in data analytics and Business Intelligence;
Demonstrated experience with the following reporting packages: Microsoft PowerBI and QlikView 12;
Experience in the following technologies is a plus: Microsoft SQL Server, SAP ERP 6.0, ServiceNow and Splunk;
Knowledge of statistics and experience using statistical tools is a plus;
Good communication skills in English are a must;
Proactive, autonomous, trustworthy, team- and results-oriented.

